properties.name: Frontier benches
properties.description: A great place to hang out and talk with people.  Lots of smokers hang out here but even if you're not a smoker, it's still fun to chill with them.

properties.name: Papa John's Pizza
properties.description: Best place for the 2 AM Saturday morning munchies.  Just be aware that everyone else knows this too.

properties.name: Tornado Alley
properties.description: This area recieves a lot of wind due to all the gusts being funneled under the skyways.  If you're sensible, avoid this area in winter, or if you're awesome, tough, and adventurous, go through it whenever you can in the winter.
